The Keiser Report  No. 105
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 21 December 2010


[sebaygo1]

Markets! Finance! JP Morgue!

Max and Stacy look at the rise of financial activism and talk about Janet Tavakoli's presentation and repairing the damage of fraud as a business model. 

In the second half Max talks to Nicole Foss about the unpopped bubble in Canada. 



The .mp3 is audio extracted from the Russia Today video.
